    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 36-39.</p><p>Divine Indemnity</p><p>At 25th level, your God grants you control over the powers of protection they have bestowed upon your blessed self.</p><p>You can expend 2 Legendary Points and use your action to give a creature within 60 feet of you immunity to all damage for up to 1 minute. You can only protect one creature in this manner at a time. The protection breaks if the target creature is ever farther than 500 feet away from you or on a different plane of existence. This counts as a magical effect of 9th level for the purposes of Tiers of Magic and uses your concentration.</p></div>",
